								<label>a. $0 - $20<input type="radio" name="a3" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>b. $21 - $50<input type="radio" name="a3" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. $51 - $100<input type="radio" name="a3" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>d. More than $100<input type="radio" name="a3" value="4" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div style="height:100%;">
								<p>5. Do you think your pet is cuter than others?</p>
								<label>a. Yes <input type="radio" name="a4" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>b. No <input type="radio" name="a4" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. I'm not sure<input type="radio" name="a4" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div style="height:100%;" margin:10px>
								<p>6. Do your pets know any tricks? If yes, can you explain?</p>
								<label>a. Yes<input type="radio" name="a5" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>b. No <input type="radio" name="a5" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. Maybe<input type="radio" name="a5" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>Explain: <textarea rows="4" cols="50" value="" name="comment" form="usrform" name="a5" id="trickExplain" onblur="getTextArea();"></textarea></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div style="height:100%;" margin:10px>
								<p>7. Do you have any online social network account?</p>
								<label>a. Yes <input type="radio" name="a6" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>b. No <input type="radio" name="a6" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. I'm not sure <input type="radio" name="a6" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div style="height:100%;" margin:10px>
								<p>8. Do you like to take pictures, videos for your pets?</p>
								<label>a. Yes <input type="radio" name="a7" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>b. No <input type="radio" name="a7" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. I'm not sure<input type="radio" name="a7" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div style="height:100%;" margin:10px>
								<p>9. How often do you shop online for your pets?</p>
								<label>a. Never<input type="radio" name="a8" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></inpjavascriput></label><br><br>
								<label>b. Rarely<input type="radio" name="a8" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. Occasionally<input type="radio" name="a8" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>d. Frequently<input type="radio" name="a8" value="4" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
						<li>
							<div style="height:100%;">
								<p>10. Would you like donate as little as $0.10 to reward your online friend pets if they are adorable/play cute/know tricks/ to show your love an generous?</p>
								<label>a. Yes <input type="radio" name="a9" value="1" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>b. No <input type="radio" name="a9" value="2" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>c. Maybe <input type="radio" name="a9" value="3" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
								<label>d. I don't know<input type="radio" name="a9" value="4" onclick="getResult();"></input></label><br><br>
							</div>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
					<%= form_for :surveyresult do |f| %>
